data.description: Welcome home to this meticulously renovated ranch in Roswell's Lake Forest! Boasting $95,000 in improvements, this 3-bed, 2-bath gem welcomes you with fantastic curb appeal and a bright, open layout. The updated eat-in kitchen features new appliances, a custom pantry design, and ample cabinet space. Experience the beauty of nature in your atrium and indulge in the luxury of a brand-new master bath. Enjoy comfort with new windows, a screened porch, and a new HVAC system. The oversized master and two spacious bedrooms provide ample living space. The landscaped yard with an irrigation system offers privacy adjacent to a wooded greenbelt. With a low HOA fee of $120/year, this home is a short distance from the 16-mile greenway, NorthPoint Parkway shopping, and GA 400. The motivated seller has recently reduced the price below appraisal and is open to considering a 2-1 buydown in interest rate. Call now for details and make this dream home yours!
